		<div id="comment_body_64187366"><p>It's a bad idea to host this in any state where the government has a history of using its political power to attack entities whose speech it doesn't like (e.g. China, Dubai, Florida, etc). These states are worthless for celebrations of art and new ideas.</p><p>Stick to free states in the future.</p></div>
	</div>

